485        - 1].Name[ret]);



486      a[ret] = tmp[ret];



487    }



488



489    ret = memcmp(&a[0], &b[0], 9);



490    if (ret == 0) {



491      fieldIdx = i;



492      exitg1 = true;



493    } else {



494      b_i++;



495    }



496  }



497



498  return fieldIdx;



499}

514  }

517static void PointCloud2Types_rosToMATLABTyp(uint8_T type, char_T mlType_data[],



518  int32_T mlType_size[2], real_T *numBytes)



519{



520  int32_T i;



521  static const char_T tmp[5] = { 'u', 'i', 'n', 't', '8' };



522



523  static const char_T tmp_0[5] = { 'i', 'n', 't', '1', '6' };



524



525  static const char_T tmp_1[6] = { 'u', 'i', 'n', 't', '1', '6' };



526



527  static const char_T tmp_2[5] = { 'i', 'n', 't', '3', '2' };



528



529  static const char_T tmp_3[6] = { 'u', 'i', 'n', 't', '3', '2' };



530



531  static const char_T tmp_4[6] = { 's', 'i', 'n', 'g', 'l', 'e' };



532



533  static const char_T tmp_5[6] = { 'd', 'o', 'u', 'b', 'l', 'e' };



534



535  switch (type) {



536   case 1:



537    mlType_size[0] = 1;



538    mlType_size[1] = 4;



539    mlType_data[0] = 'i';



540    mlType_data[1] = 'n';



541    mlType_data[2] = 't';



542    mlType_data[3] = '8';



543    *numBytes = 1.0;



544    break;



545



546   case 2:



547    mlType_size[0] = 1;



548    mlType_size[1] = 5;



549    for (i = 0; i < 5; i++) {



550      mlType_data[i] = tmp[i];



551    }



552



553    *numBytes = 1.0;



554    break;



555



556   case 3:



557    mlType_size[0] = 1;



558    mlType_size[1] = 5;



559    for (i = 0; i < 5; i++) {



560      mlType_data[i] = tmp_0[i];



561    }



562



563    *numBytes = 2.0;



564    break;



565



566   case 4:



567    mlType_size[0] = 1;



568    mlType_size[1] = 6;



569    for (i = 0; i < 6; i++) {



570      mlType_data[i] = tmp_1[i];



571    }



572



573    *numBytes = 2.0;



574    break;



575



576   case 5:



577    mlType_size[0] = 1;



578    mlType_size[1] = 5;



579    for (i = 0; i < 5; i++) {



580      mlType_data[i] = tmp_2[i];



581    }



582



583    *numBytes = 4.0;



584    break;



585



586   case 6:



587    mlType_size[0] = 1;



588    mlType_size[1] = 6;



589    for (i = 0; i < 6; i++) {



590      mlType_data[i] = tmp_3[i];



591    }



592



593    *numBytes = 4.0;



594    break;



595



596   case 7:



597    mlType_size[0] = 1;



598    mlType_size[1] = 6;



599    for (i = 0; i < 6; i++) {



600      mlType_data[i] = tmp_4[i];



601    }



602



603    *numBytes = 4.0;



604    break;



605



606   case 8:



607    mlType_size[0] = 1;



608    mlType_size[1] = 6;



609    for (i = 0; i < 6; i++) {



610      mlType_data[i] = tmp_5[i];



611    }



612



613    *numBytes = 8.0;



614    break;



615  }



616}

618real_T rt_roundd_snf(real_T u)



619{



620  real_T y;



621  if (fabs(u) < 4.503599627370496E+15) {



622    if (u >= 0.5) {



623      y = floor(u + 0.5);



624    } else if (u > -0.5) {



625      y = u * 0.0;



626    } else {



627      y = ceil(u - 0.5);



628    }



629  } else {



630    y = u;



631  }



632



633  return y;



634}

636static void optimal_path_t2_bsxfun(const real_T a_data[], const int32_T *a_size,



637  const real_T b_data[], const int32_T b_size[2], real_T c_data[], int32_T



638  c_size[2])



639{



640  int32_T bcoef;



641  int32_T ib;



642  int32_T d;



643  int32_T k;



644  int32_T acoef;



645  int32_T k_0;



646  int32_T csz_idx_0;



647  csz_idx_0 = *a_size;



648  c_size[0] = *a_size;



649  c_size[1] = b_size[1];



650  if (*a_size != 0) {



651    bcoef = (b_size[1] != 1);



652    d = b_size[1];



653    for (k = 0; k < d; k++) {



654      ib = bcoef * k;



655      acoef = (*a_size != 1);



656      for (k_0 = 0; k_0 < csz_idx_0; k_0++) {



657        c_data[k_0 + *a_size * k] = a_data[acoef * k_0] + b_data[ib];



658      }



659    }



660  }



661}

663static void PointCloud2Reader_getByteIndexF(const



664  c_ros_slros_internal_block_Po_T *pc, uint32_T fieldIdx, const real_T



665  pointIndices[650000], real_T byteIdx_data[], int32_T byteIdx_size[2],



666  boolean_T pointIdxIsValid[650000])



667{



668  int32_T pc_size;



669  boolean_T e;



670  boolean_T f;



671  uint32_T qY;



672  int32_T byteIdx_size_tmp;



673  PointCloud2BusWrapper_get_Data(pc, optimal_path_t2_B.b_data,



674    &optimal_path_t2_B.b_size);



675  optimal_path_t2_B.u = static_cast<real_T>(optimal_path_t2_B.b_size) /



676    static_cast<real_T>(pc->BusStruct.PointStep);



677  if (optimal_path_t2_B.u < 0.0) {



678    optimal_path_t2_B.u = ceil(optimal_path_t2_B.u);



679  } else {



680    optimal_path_t2_B.u = floor(optimal_path_t2_B.u);



681  }



682



683  optimal_path_t2_B.numPointsActual = mul_u32_sat(pc->BusStruct.Height,



684    pc->BusStruct.Width);



685  if ((!rtIsNaN(optimal_path_t2_B.u)) && (optimal_path_t2_B.numPointsActual >



686       optimal_path_t2_B.u)) {



687    if (optimal_path_t2_B.u >= 0.0) {



688      optimal_path_t2_B.numPointsActual = static_cast<uint32_T>



689        (optimal_path_t2_B.u);



690    } else {



691      optimal_path_t2_B.numPointsActual = 0U;



692    }



693  }



694



695  PointCloud2Types_rosToMATLABTyp(pc->BusStruct.Fields[static_cast<int32_T>



696    (fieldIdx) - 1].Datatype, optimal_path_t2_B.unusedU0_data,



697    optimal_path_t2_B.unusedU0_size, &optimal_path_t2_B.u);

699  byteIdx_size_tmp = static_cast<int32_T>(optimal_path_t2_B.u);



700  byteIdx_size[1] = byteIdx_size_tmp;



701  optimal_path_t2_B.loop_ub_f = 650000 * byteIdx_size_tmp - 1;



702  if (0 <= optimal_path_t2_B.loop_ub_f) {

704           (real_T));



705  }

708  for (optimal_path_t2_B.b_i = 0; optimal_path_t2_B.b_i < 650000;

710    e = (0.0 < pointIndices[optimal_path_t2_B.b_i]);



711    f = (pointIndices[optimal_path_t2_B.b_i] <=



712         optimal_path_t2_B.numPointsActual);



713    pointIdxIsValid[optimal_path_t2_B.b_i] = (e && f);



714    if (e && f) {



715      byteIdx_size_tmp++;



716    }



717



718    optimal_path_t2_B.e[optimal_path_t2_B.b_i] = e;



719    optimal_path_t2_B.f[optimal_path_t2_B.b_i] = f;



720  }



721



722  optimal_path_t2_B.loop_ub_f = byteIdx_size_tmp;



723  byteIdx_size_tmp = 0;



724  for (optimal_path_t2_B.b_i = 0; optimal_path_t2_B.b_i < 650000;



725       optimal_path_t2_B.b_i++) {



726    if (optimal_path_t2_B.e[optimal_path_t2_B.b_i] &&



727        optimal_path_t2_B.f[optimal_path_t2_B.b_i]) {



728      optimal_path_t2_B.g_data[byteIdx_size_tmp] = optimal_path_t2_B.b_i + 1;



729      byteIdx_size_tmp++;



730    }



731  }



732



733  if (rtIsNaN(optimal_path_t2_B.u)) {



734    optimal_path_t2_B.y_size[0] = 1;



735    optimal_path_t2_B.y_size[1] = 1;



736    optimal_path_t2_B.y_data_b[0] = (rtNaN);



737  } else {



738    optimal_path_t2_B.y_size[0] = 1;



739    optimal_path_t2_B.b_i = static_cast<int32_T>(floor(optimal_path_t2_B.u - 1.0));



740    optimal_path_t2_B.y_size[1] = optimal_path_t2_B.b_i + 1;



741    for (byteIdx_size_tmp = 0; byteIdx_size_tmp <= optimal_path_t2_B.b_i;



742         byteIdx_size_tmp++) {



743      optimal_path_t2_B.y_data_b[byteIdx_size_tmp] = static_cast<real_T>



744        (byteIdx_size_tmp) + 1.0;



745    }



746  }



747



748  byteIdx_size_tmp = 0;



749  for (optimal_path_t2_B.b_i = 0; optimal_path_t2_B.b_i < 650000;



750       optimal_path_t2_B.b_i++) {



751    if (optimal_path_t2_B.e[optimal_path_t2_B.b_i] &&



752        optimal_path_t2_B.f[optimal_path_t2_B.b_i]) {



753      optimal_path_t2_B.i_data[byteIdx_size_tmp] = optimal_path_t2_B.b_i + 1;



754      byteIdx_size_tmp++;



755    }



756  }



757



758  pc_size = optimal_path_t2_B.loop_ub_f;



759  for (byteIdx_size_tmp = 0; byteIdx_size_tmp < optimal_path_t2_B.loop_ub_f;



760       byteIdx_size_tmp++) {



761    optimal_path_t2_B.numPointsActual = pc->BusStruct.Fields[static_cast<int32_T>



762      (fieldIdx) - 1].Offset;



763    optimal_path_t2_B.u = rt_roundd_snf



764      (pointIndices[optimal_path_t2_B.g_data[byteIdx_size_tmp] - 1] - 1.0);



765    if (optimal_path_t2_B.u < 4.294967296E+9) {



766      if (optimal_path_t2_B.u >= 0.0) {



767        qY = static_cast<uint32_T>(optimal_path_t2_B.u);



768      } else {



769        qY = 0U;



770      }



771    } else {



772      qY = MAX_uint32_T;



773    }



774



775    qY = optimal_path_t2_B.numPointsActual + /*MW:OvSatOk*/ mul_u32_sat



776      (pc->BusStruct.PointStep, qY);



777    if (qY < optimal_path_t2_B.numPointsActual) {



778      qY = MAX_uint32_T;



779    }



780



781    optimal_path_t2_B.pc_data[byteIdx_size_tmp] = qY;



782  }



783



784  optimal_path_t2_bsxfun(optimal_path_t2_B.pc_data, &pc_size,



785    optimal_path_t2_B.y_data_b, optimal_path_t2_B.y_size,



786    optimal_path_t2_B.tmp_data, optimal_path_t2_B.unusedU0_size);



787  optimal_path_t2_B.loop_ub_f = optimal_path_t2_B.unusedU0_size[1];



788  for (byteIdx_size_tmp = 0; byteIdx_size_tmp < optimal_path_t2_B.loop_ub_f;



789       byteIdx_size_tmp++) {



790    optimal_path_t2_B.b_i = optimal_path_t2_B.unusedU0_size[0];



791    for (optimal_path_t2_B.i = 0; optimal_path_t2_B.i < optimal_path_t2_B.b_i;



792         optimal_path_t2_B.i++) {



793      byteIdx_data[(optimal_path_t2_B.i_data[optimal_path_t2_B.i] + 650000 *



794                    byteIdx_size_tmp) - 1] =



795        optimal_path_t2_B.tmp_data[optimal_path_t2_B.unusedU0_size[0] *



796        byteIdx_size_tmp + optimal_path_t2_B.i];



797    }



798  }



799}

801static void optimal_path_t2_typecast(const uint8_T x_data[], const int32_T



802  *x_size, real32_T y_data[], int32_T *y_size)



803{

806    ny = 0;



807  } else {



808    ny = *x_size >> 2;



809  }



810



811  *y_size = ny;



812  memcpy((void *)&y_data[0], (void *)&x_data[0], (uint32_T)((size_t)ny * sizeof



813          (real32_T)));



814}

816static boolean_T optimal_path_t2_any(const boolean_T x[650000])



817{



818  boolean_T y;



819  int32_T b_k;



820  boolean_T exitg1;



821  y = false;



822  b_k = 0;



823  exitg1 = false;



824  while ((!exitg1) && (b_k < 650000)) {



825    if (!x[b_k]) {



826      b_k++;



827    } else {



828      y = true;



829      exitg1 = true;



830    }



831  }



832



833  return y;



834}

836static void PointCloud2Reader_readFieldFrom(const uint8_T data_data[], const

857      b_trueCount++;



858    }

865        static_cast<int32_T>(byteIdx_data[(650000 * d_size +

867    }



868  }

1327real32_T rt_roundf_snf(real32_T u)



1328{



1329  real32_T y;



1330  if (static_cast<real32_T>(fabs(static_cast<real_T>(u))) < 8.388608E+6F) {



1331    if (u >= 0.5F) {



1332      y = static_cast<real32_T>(floor(static_cast<real_T>((u + 0.5F))));



1333    } else if (u > -0.5F) {



1334      y = u * 0.0F;



1335    } else {



1336      y = static_cast<real32_T>(ceil(static_cast<real_T>((u - 0.5F))));



1337    }



1338  } else {



1339    y = u;



1340  }



1341



1342  return y;



1343}

1345// Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/MATLAB Function8'



1346static boolean_T optimal_path_t2_sortLE(const int16_T v_data[], const int32_T



1347  v_size[2], const int32_T dir_data[], const int32_T dir_size[2], int32_T idx1,



1348  int32_T idx2)



1349{



1350  boolean_T p;



1351  int16_T v1;



1352  int16_T v2;



1353  int32_T k;



1354  int32_T v1_tmp;



1355  boolean_T exitg1;



1356  p = true;



1357  k = 0;



1358  exitg1 = false;



1359  while ((!exitg1) && (k <= dir_size[1] - 1)) {



1360    v1_tmp = (dir_data[k] - 1) * v_size[0];



1361    v1 = v_data[(v1_tmp + idx1) - 1];



1362    v2 = v_data[(v1_tmp + idx2) - 1];



1363    if (v1 != v2) {



1364      p = (v1 <= v2);



1365      exitg1 = true;



1366    } else {



1367      k++;



1368    }



1369  }



1370



1371  return p;



1372}
